\v 54 Ngakho uJesu kabesahamba obala phakathi kwamaJuda\x + 7.1. 12.36.\x*, kodwa wasuka lapho waya elizweni eliseduze lenkangala\x + Mat. 3.1.\x*, emzini othiwa yiEfrayimi\x + 2 Lan. 13.19.\x*, wasehlala khona labafundi bakhe.
