\v 55 Laselisondele iphasika lamaJuda\x + 2.13. 5.1. 6.4. 12.1,12,20. 13.1. 18.28,39. 19.14. Mat. 26.2.\x*; labanengi abavela emaphandleni benyukela eJerusalema lingakafiki iphasika\x + Luka 2.4.\x*, ukuze bazihlambulule\x + Nani 9.10. 2 Lan. 30.17,18. Seb. 21.24,26. 24.18.\x*.
\v 56 Ngakho bamdinga uJesu, bekhulumisana bemi ethempelini \add besithi\add*: Licabangani? Lithi isibili kayikuza emkhosini yini\x + 7.11. 11.8.\x*?
\v 57 Kodwa bonke abapristi abakhulu labaFarisi babekhuphe umlayo wokuthi uba ekhona owaziyo lapho akhona, akubike ukuze bambambe.